		<h2>What?</h2>
		<p>
			DigitalKanban is a small but simple digital Kanban board.<br />
			Kanban is a widely common lean management method in companies for software development.<br />
			There are few rules to respect, but the rest of the rule set is free to choice and can be adapt to your personal process.<br />
		</p>
		<p>
			Most of the companies have a physical board in the office. This is a very good way, but has some disadvantages. For example the work on one with distributed teams.<br />
			With DigitalKanban distributed teams can work on one project with one Kanban board together! DigitalKanban isn`t bind to a physical location :)
		</p>
		<p>
			The list of features is quite basic but useful:<br />
			<ul>
				<li>Create, edit and delete a unlimited numbers of users</li>
				<li>Two usergroups (Administrators and users)</li>
				<li>Create, edit and delete a unlimited numbers of Kanban boards</li>
				<li>Create and delete a unlimited numbers of Kanbans (single tickets)</li>
				<li>Drag and drop to move the issue through your whole process</li>
				<li>Create and delete a unlimited numbers of columns per Kanban board</li>
				<li>Respect WiP (Limits) per column</li>
				<li>... and much more!</li>
			</ul>
		</p>
