			During this time the company where is Andy working introduced the agile project management way "<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanban_(development)" title="Kanban at Wikipedia">Kanban</a>".<br />
			The idea was born. Lets build a small and simple digital kanban board to combine all needs by out professor.<br />
		</p>
